---
title: Chicken and Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto Orzo with Spinach, Zucchini and Parmesan
description: A big bowl of pasta screams comfort! Tonight's orzo is kicked up with sun-dried tomato pesto and Parmesan cheese and studded with zucchini and spinach. Top that bowl off with a garlicky chicken breast and you have a simple and delicious dinner in!
